document_data.mainbody:
Canthrell was an elongated island found between Norheim and Norland in the Moonshae Isles.
Canthrells was located between the Sea of Moonshae on its southeastern shores and the Trackless Sea to the northwest. It was the largest of a series of islands that almost joined Norheim and Norland in the northwest Moonshae Isles. Canthrell was  long, but only  wide at its widest point.
* Threlloch
